---
title: Sticky Pork Bites with Roasted Sweet Potatoes
description: Pork tenderloin gets a quick chop, followed by a dusting of cornstarch to create the ultimate crisp coating on these bites before they get tossed in sticky DIY honey garlic sauce. Roasted sweet potatoes and fresh apple adorn the chopped salad with toasted almonds bringing the perfect crunch!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bouchees-de-porc-miel-et-ail-00cf8f07.jpg
